=== 支持 ===
截止2022年3月為止，已有146個國家或地區支持一帶一路倡議，當中139個國家已與中國簽署諒解備忘錄。<ref name=":2" />

中國的官方立場是認為「一带一路」倡议坚持共商、共建、共享的原则，努力实现沿线区域基础设施更加完善，更加安全高效，以形成更高水準的陆海空交流网路。同时使投资贸易的便利化水準更有效的提升，建立高品質、高标准的自由贸易区域网。以使沿线各国经济联系更加紧密，政治互信更加的深入，人文交流更加的广泛<ref>[https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=2997650 What is One Belt One Road? A Surplus Recycling Mechanism Approach] {{Wayback|url=https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=2997650|date=20180603013419}}. Social Science Research Network (SSRN).</ref>又認為該倡議為商品提供了市場，改善了基礎設施，創造了就業機會，刺激了工業化，擴大了技術轉讓，從而使一帶一路國家受益。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Revisiting the Resurrected Debate About Chinese Neocolonialism|url=https://thediplomat.com/2018/02/revisiting-the-resurrected-debate-about-chinese-neocolonialism/|access-date=2022-04-14|work=thediplomat.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123195340/https://thediplomat.com/2018/02/revisiting-the-resurrected-debate-about-chinese-neocolonialism/}}</ref>並且否认一帶一路為「中國版[[马歇尔计划|马歇尔计划]]」或「[[債務陷阱外交|債務陷阱外交]]」的說法<ref name="udn20150216">{{cite news|url=http://blogrushinews.blogspot.tw/2015/02/3_16.html|title=一帶一路計畫 傳3月兩會公布|work=聯合新聞網|date=2015-02-16|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2017-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028071450/http://blogrushinews.blogspot.tw/2015/02/3_16.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

俄羅斯是中國早期的合作夥伴，目前俄中兩國共有天然氣管道、極地絲綢之路等150個共同項目。2015年3月，俄羅斯第一副總理伊戈爾·舒瓦洛夫就說︰「俄羅斯不應將絲綢之路經濟帶視為對其傳統區域勢力範圍的威脅，而是應將其視為歐亞經濟聯盟的機遇。」<ref>{{Cite web|title=BRI transforming world economic order|url=https://asiatimes.com/2019/04/bri-transforming-world-economic-order/|access-date=2022-04-12|date=2019-04-25|last=Ehret|first=Matthew J. L.|work=Asia Times|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419050016/https://asiatimes.com/2019/04/bri-transforming-world-economic-order/}}</ref>

2016年6月，波蘭總統安傑伊·杜達會見中國國家主席習近平，稱波蘭企業將從「一帶一路」倡議中受益匪淺。<ref>{{Cite web|title=President Duda hopes Poland will become China's gateway to Europe|url=https://www.president.pl/news/president-duda-hopes-poland-will-become-chinas-gateway-to-europe,36162|access-date=2022-04-12|date=2016-06-20|work=Oficjalna strona Prezydenta Rzeczypospolitej Polskiej|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419050016/https://www.president.pl/news/president-duda-hopes-poland-will-become-chinas-gateway-to-europe,36162}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=President Duda sends sympathy message to President Xi Jinping|url=https://www.thefirstnews.com/article/president-duda-sends-sympathy-message-to-president-xi-jinping-10277|access-date=2022-04-12|work=www.thefirstnews.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414180434/https://www.thefirstnews.com/article/president-duda-sends-sympathy-message-to-president-xi-jinping-10277}}</ref>杜達與習近平簽署戰略夥伴關係宣言，重申波中視對方為長期戰略夥伴。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Xi welcomes Chinese freight train to 'strategic partner' Poland|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-poland-china-xi-idUKKCN0Z6205|newspaper=Reuters|date=2016-06-20|accessdate=2022-04-12|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419050026/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-poland-china-xi-idUKKCN0Z6205}}</ref>

